## API Recv [/api/recv/{endpoint}/{metric}/{ts}/{step}/{dstype}/{value}]

+ Parameters
    + endpoint: `host1` (string) - Name of an endpoint.
    + metric: `cpu.user` (string) - Name of a metric.
    + ts: `1456286162` (number) - Timestamp.
    + step: `host` (60) - must be greater than or equal to 30 seconds.
