| 34 | team_api |     |        0 |                   0 |                    0 |                  0 |                   0 |
+----+----------+-----+----------+---------------------+----------------------+--------------------+---------------------+
1 row in set (0.10 sec)
```
and "falcon_portal.tpl" table is updated by setting value of "action_id" field to 34:
```
mysql> select * from tpl where tpl_name="template_api";
